project_info_title: Contemporary coastal living at Dubai Islands
project_info_text:
Wynwood Residence by Imtiaz Developments introduces a refined residential concept on Dubai Islands, where modern architecture meets relaxed island surroundings.

The collection includes 1 to 3-bedroom apartments and spacious duplexes with expansive terraces. Floor-to-ceiling windows, smart home features, and premium finishes enhance everyday comfort, while the vibrant seafront setting offers residents a balanced lifestyle between urban energy and coastal serenity.
amenities_title: Infrastructure and landscaping of the residential complex
project_summary_subtitle: Modern apartments and duplexes with ocean views
map_text: Situated on Dubai Islands, Wynwood Residence enjoys a privileged waterfront setting surrounded by beaches, promenades, and emerging lifestyle destinations. The community offers convenient access to Deira, Downtown Dubai, and Dubai International Airport while maintaining a tranquil island atmosphere.
footer_tagline: Refined beachfront living at Dubai Islands
